2016.06.24
This is sourcecode of DCASE Challenge 2016 Task 1. http://www.cs.tut.fi/sgn/arg/dcase2016/task-acoustic-scene-classification
Using Mel + DNN achieve 77% average accuracy using 4 fold cross validation on development dataset. 

THIS CODE IS BSD LISCENCED. YOU CAN USE AND MODIFY IT AS YOU WISH. 
AUTHOR: QIUQIANG KONG, q.kong@surrey.ac.uk
CVSSP, UNIVERSITY OF SURREY

======================================

Pre-requiste:
librosa
Hat (https://github.com/qiuqiangkong/Hat)

Usage:
------ Preparation ------
1. modify the paths of dataset in config.py, modify paths of HAT in every file. 

------ Development Cross Validation ------
1. run prepareData.py 		Calculate features for development data
2. run main_dnn.py 		Train model on cross validation of development data
3. run recognize.py 		Generate results and evaluate on cross validation data

------ Generate Results of Private Data ------
1. run prepareData_eva.py	Calculate features for evaluation data
2. run main_dnn_eva.py		Train model on all development data
3. run recognize_eva.py		Generate Results of private data
